title: The Commanded Blessing | Joel Osteen

description:
God has a commanded blessing prepared that will bring you to a new level of supernatural increase. His favor will cause you to rise from lack into abundance.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
